{"tid":190594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國北方多個城市持續中至重度空氣污染","createTime":"2017-04-07T08:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T09:33:31.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ad1b8b81a0ea7b0a561c1cbb192b6e7c4215fbf","tid":190594,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T08:26:51.000Z","msg":"2017-04-07 14:30<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170407/_2017040714213479525_detail.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170407%2F_2017040714213479525_detail.jpg&h=0d1f19f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【星島日報報道】石家莊、邯鄲、長春等城市空氣質量，早上出現重度污染。最新預報顯示，受大氣擴散條件持續不利影響，北京、石家莊、保定等地預計將出現短時中至重度污染。<br />\n　　根據中國環境監測總站與長三角、珠三角區域空氣質量預報中心和相關省級空氣質量預報部門，基於現有污染源監測、環境空氣質量實時監測、大氣污染過程模擬分析和聯合會商，預計今日至9日，全國大部地區空氣質量以良至輕度污染為主，華北局部地區中至重度污染過程有望在8日前後開始緩解。<br />\n　　中國環境監測總站發佈重污染過程提示顯示，7日，大氣擴散條件持續不利，部分城市可能出現短時中至重度污染，影響範圍包括北京、石家莊、保定、廊坊、邢台、衡水、邯鄲、鄭州、安陽、鶴壁、新鄉、焦作、濮陽、開封、洛陽、德州、聊城、菏澤、晉城等。<br />\n　　今日，京津冀及周邊區域北部以良至輕度污染為主，北京、天津、河北中南部、山西南部和山東西部以輕至中度污染為主，可能出現短時重度污染。<br />\n　　預報認為，8日至9日，受冷空氣影響，空氣質量將自北向南逐步好轉，京津冀及周邊區域北部空氣質量優良，區域中南部以良至輕度污染為主。其中8日，受污染傳輸影響，河北南部和河南可能出現短時中至重度污染。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/377767-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%97%E6%96%B9%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%8B%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E4%B8%AD%E8%87%B3%E9%87%8D%E5%BA%A6%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F377767-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2587%25B3%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E6%259F%2593&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGosn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=6037a83f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F377767-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2587%25B3%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E6%259F%2593&h=11d9d6e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/377767-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%97%E6%96%B9%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%8B%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E4%B8%AD%E8%87%B3%E9%87%8D%E5%BA%A6%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93</a>"},{"pid":"5efc2cc45b90ac6f9ae3e3b891b25f3239fb04e2","tid":190594,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T08:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916063c23ef93d3981760fb2a013f9a636c0392c","tid":190594,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2dfff8cb99ed706ef77fad613dbad1370c4ce4","tid":190594,"uid":22424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:33:31.000Z","msg":"新聞黎既咩？？"}]}